# DVT Project Rules

**Description**: Global project rules that apply to all work in dvt-ce.

## Repository Context

- **Repository**: `git@github.com:heshamh96/dvt-ce.git`
- **Default Branch**: `new_dev` (all development happens here)
- **Branch Flow**: new_dev → feature branches → PRs back to new_dev
- **Packages**: dvt-ce (dbt.* + dvt.*) and dvt-adapters (dbt.adapters.* + dbt.include.*, 13 engines)
- **No external dbt**: No dbt-core or dbt-adapters from PyPI; everything is vendored in dvt-ce

